headline: Quanta Services Announces Fourth Quarter And Full-Year 2025 Earnings Release & Webcast Schedule
summary: Quanta Services, Inc. (NYSE: PWR) announced today that it will release its fourth quarter and full-year 2025 financial results on Thursday, February 19, 2026, before the market opens. In conjunction with the press release, Quanta has scheduled a webcast and conference call for 9:00 a.m. Eastern time on Thursday, February 19, 2026.
